a perk of the job.

08:07.820 --> 08:09.014
(scoffs)
Okay.

08:09.050 --> 08:10.881
Well, I'm your black
shield tonight, okay?

08:10.920 --> 08:12.888
(cell phone buzzes)
It's Roger Hailman.

08:12.920 --> 08:15.514
Yeah, he's my friend
at the courthouse.

08:15.560 --> 08:17.528
Uh-huh.

08:17.560 --> 08:19.824
Roger, hey, what's up?

08:19.860 --> 08:21.851
ANNOUNCER: Ladies and gentlemen,
please take your seats.

08:21.900 --> 08:23.595
